{
"application": "slurm",
"details": {
"software": [
"miniconda3",
"cuda",
"torchrun",
"deepspeed",
"wandb",
"nvidia-smi"
],
"resources": {
"cpu": 3,
"gpu": 4,
"memory": "128G",
"storage": "/ukp-storage-1/fang"
},
"libraries": [
"bert",
"wikipedia",
"bert-large-uncased",
"adamw",
"gelu"
],
"script": "run_mlm.py",
"configuration": {
"model_type": "bert",
"dataset_name": "wikipedia",
"dataset_config_name": "20200501.en",

"gradient_accumulation_steps": 4,
"per_device_eval_batch_size": 256,
"do_train": true,
"do_eval": true,
"lr_schedule": "step step step",
"max_steps": 23000,
"curve": "linear linear linear",
"warmup_proportion": 0.01,
"adam_beta1": 0.9,
"adam_beta2": 0.98,
"half_precision_backend": "auto",
"num_train_epochs": 100,
"optimizer": "adamw",
"report_to": "wandb",
"save_total_limit": 20,
"logging_steps": 250,
"save_steps": 1000,
"max_seq_length": 128,
"learning_rate": 0.0007,
"preprocessing_num_workers": 15,
"output_dir": "./outputs/acabert/original/0.0007/12layers/adamw/deepnet-0.01warm",
"rational_layers": "''",
"approx_func": "gelu",
"run_name": "academicbert-original-12layers-0.0007-adamw-deepnet-0.01warm",
"weight_decay": 0.01,
"academicBERT": true,
"fp16": true,
"evaluation_strategy": "steps",

"eval_steps": 250,
"max_grad_norm": 0,
"max_eval_samples": 50000

}
